"The Barbarian King is the Great Horde's ruthless monarch, ruling over his "
"subjects with an iron fist. Though he spends most of his time on his skull-"
"decorated throne, he can easily beat just about any opponent in one-on-one "
"melee combat, or groups of inexperienced soldiers. He always dreamed of "
"conquering the Jungle of Life (with it's vast natural resources), stopping "
"at nothing to make his dream a reality."
