"Roc Masters are unrivaled aerial warriors among the Barbarian horde, "
"boasting decades of expertise in handling the majestic rocs. Having spent "
"countless hours training and bonding with these noble birds of prey, they "
"have reached the pinnacle of aerial combat prowess. With graceful ease, they "
"pilot their roc towards the battlefield, their sharp eyes scanning the "
"horizon for potential targets. As they swoop down, their mighty roc's claws "
"effortlessly rip enemies to shreds. The Roc Master himself wields a crossbow "
"and a bolas, for wounding or immobilizing foes safely from above. If you "
"believe you are safe from the Barbarians' wrath in the skies, you are sorely "
"mistaken."
