msgid ""
"In the middle of the Jungle of Life lies the Great Bog, dark and marshy. It "
"is said that many a creature make their homes there.\n"
"\n"
"The saurians of the Dark Blood tribe are known to capture and tame the Bog’s "
"giant Toads, riding their backs and using them as war elephants of sorts; it "
"is known that they use special lures to make the Toads strike enemies with "
"their long, sticky tongues."
