#. [unit_type]: id=EoMa_Mirrorshield, race=human, type=fire,cold,arcane
#: Era_of_Magic/units/Sky_Kingdom/Mirrorshield.cfg:42
msgid ""
"Innovative magic mirrors are a hallmark of the Sky Kingdom, capable of "
"absorbing and deflecting magical spells. One fateful day, one such mirror "
"was stolen by cunning Mystic Warrior with the intent of selling it on a "
"black market to pay off some debts he accrued. Before he could stash the "
"mirror, he was summoned on an expedition, during which he faced a life-or-"
"death situation. When his leader was attacked and almost killed by enemy "
"mages, the warrior acted swiftly, pulling out the mirror from his backpack "
"and using it to protect himself and his comrades. The mirror's defensive "
"capabilities proved crucial, repelling the attackers and saving the group "
"from certain doom.\n"
"\n"
"The warrior's bravery and quick thinking earned him a reprieve from the "
"Master Council, who otherwise would have punished him for stealing the "
"valuable artifact. Instead, the Guru intervened on the warrior's behalf, "
"pardoning him, paying off his debts and granting him permission to keep the "
"mirror as a memento. From this encounter, the Mirrorshield Division was born "
"– a specialized unit equipped with specially crafted reinforced mirrors that "
"combine magic-deflecting properties with formidable melee weapons. These "
"elite warriors are sent on the most dangerous expeditions, and their unique "
"arsenal gives them a major advantage against powerful magic-using foes."
msgstr ""

