#: Era_of_Magic/units/Tharis/Black_Orb.cfg:16
msgid ""
"'Black Orbs' are electrically conductive crystal spheres that have been "
"imbued with life by Great Warlocks. These magical constructs are capable of "
"flight, thanks to the careful balance of energy within their hollow "
"interiors. By channeling occult power from their masters, the Black Orbs can "
"sustain themselves indefinitely, illuminated by a soft, ethereal glow.\n"
"\n"
"As scouting devices, the Black Orbs excel at detecting subtle changes in the "
"environment, sensing even the faintest traces of magic or hidden foes. Their "
"keen sensory abilities allow them to navigate unseen paths and avoid "
"detection, making them indispensable tools for covert operations.\n"
"\n"
"When threatened, they can deliver a bolt of lightning-fast justice upon "
"their enemies, unleashing a burst of dark energy stored within their "
"crystalline structures that can even kill smaller targets."
msgstr ""

