#. [unit_type]: id=EoMa_Dark_Commander, race=eoma_tharis
#: Era_of_Magic/units/Tharis/Dark_Commander.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Tharis warriors who have proven themselves through bravery and leadership "
"are often promoted to the rank of Dark Commander, exchanging their enchanted "
"daggers for spears imbued with fire magic. These powerful individuals stand "
"at least a head taller than their comrades, with broad shoulders and "
"imposing physiques that command respect. Despite their fearsome appearance, "
"however, Dark Commanders are known for their calm and collected demeanor on "
"the battlefield, inspiring their followers with their confidence and "
"authority.\n"
"\n"
"In addition to their prowess in melee combat, Dark Commanders possess a "
"limited ability to wield basic fire magic. While they may not be adept at "
"casting spells, they can still harness the power of flames to devastating "
"effect by imbuing their spears with fiery energy unleashing explosive bursts "
"of heat upon their enemies. With training and practice, they might even "
"develop greater control over this aspect of their powers, becoming truly "
"formidable mages on the battlefield."
msgstr ""

