#: Era_of_Magic/units/Tharis/Dark_Hunter.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Dark hunters embody everything that Tharis stands for - stealthy, deadly, "
"and unrelenting. They move with a quiet grace, striking from the shadows "
"like ghosts, taking down unsuspecting foes with ease. Their training allows "
"them to exploit any weakness in their opponents' defenses, whether it be a "
"gap in their formation or a momentary lapse in concentration. Against living "
"enemies, they are a serious threat. However, their effectiveness against non-"
"living enemies is more limited, as they are immune to the poisoned thrown "
"daggers favored by dark hunters themselves. Despite this limitation, they "
"remain one of the most feared and respected warrior classes in all of Tharis"
msgstr ""

