#. [unit_type]: id=EoMa_Dark_Wizard, race=eoma_tharis
#: Era_of_Magic/units/Tharis/Dark_Wizard.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Aspiring sorcerers who have honed their craft through dedication and merit "
"gradually advance within the ranks of Tharis' arcane elite, assuming roles "
"as apprentices under esteemed Great Warlocks. Some individuals, however, "
"choose to supplement their main occupation by mentoring promising novices on "
"a part-time basis. While still distant from the pinnacle of Great Warlock "
"rank, Dark Wizards possess significantly increased magical prowess compared "
"to their peers, bridging the gap towards eventual mastery. A crucial factor "
"in their accelerated growth lies in their possession of potent magical "
"staves, which amplify their innate abilities and hasten their ascent towards "
"true mastery."
msgstr ""

