#: Era_of_Magic/units/Tharis/Great_Hydra.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Risen from the depths of the underground tunnels like a nightmarish "
"manifestation, this towering, mature Great Hydra brooks no opposition. Its "
"sheer size and ferocity make it a terror beyond compare, with three twisted "
"heads, each one seemingly more malevolent than the last, the beast stalks "
"its prey with unrelenting determination, leaving a trail of destruction in "
"its wake. Those who have witnessed this abomination up close live only to "
"bear witness to its fury, their screams and pleas for mercy lost to the "
"echoes of the caverns."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type]: id=EoMa_Great_Warlock, race=eoma_tharis
