#: Era_of_Magic/units/Tharis/Matriarch_of_Frost.cfg:24
msgid ""
"Unlike their brethren, who prefer to dwell among others of their kind, these "
"powerful witches choose to isolate themselves in remote, inhospitable "
"regions of the world. Years of residing in such harsh environments, combined "
"with intense study and practice of dark magic, grant them the ability to "
"manipulate the very fabric of reality itself.\n"
"\n"
"Whenever one of these Matriarchs emerges from their seclusion, they exude a "
"palpable chill that can drop temperatures to dangerously low levels, even in "
"the midst of warm climates. This unnerving aura extends far beyond their "
"physical presence, infusing the air with an icy energy that can petrify or "
"freeze any living thing caught too close. The mere proximity to a Matriarch "
"of Frost can cause water to solidify into ice crystals, rendering flames "
"impotent against their will.\n"
"\n"
"Despite their fearsome reputation, the Matriarchs of Frost are not devoid of "
"compassion. They periodically leave their glacial abodes to join the Tharis "
"in their crusades, bringing forth a maelstrom of frigid chaos that shakes "
"the foundations of the earth. In battle, they prove to be an unstoppable "
"force, their powers amplified by the adrenaline and ferocity of combat. As "
"long as they remain loyal to the Tharis, no foe stands a chance against the "
"wrath of a Matriarch of Frost."
msgstr ""

